data.description: Building a Web App with JavaScript & jQuery: Free Workshop Monday, December 19th from 6:30pm to 8:30pm Learning JavaScript doesn't have to be hard. Join us as we build and deploy a simple web app. We'll focus on the basics of JavaScript for web applications, specifically using jQuery to create interactive features. The class is free, open to beginners and those already learning JavaScript, and 100% hands-on. Just bring a laptop - we'll provide refreshments. ----- Interested in becoming a web developer? Visit Thinkful for more information on our bootcamps and upcoming Raleigh classes and events.
